# create a pod
    kubectl apply -f task-3 

2.	Check the current status of the Pod
    kubectl get pods
    NAME      READY   STATUS    RESTARTS   AGE
    web-pod   1/1     Running   0          6s
3- Show detailed information about the Pod
    kubectl describe pod web-pod 
4- delete a pod 
    kubectl delete pod web-pod 
    pod "web-pod" deleted from default namespace
